com.pranavpandey.android.dynamic.engine.receiver

Class DynamicStateReceiver

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.BroadcastReceiver
      • com.pranavpandey.android.dynamic.engine.receiver.DynamicStateReceiver

  • public class DynamicStateReceiver
extends BroadcastReceiver
    Broadcast receiver to listen call events. It has been already added in the manifest and should be registered dynamically at the runtime.

    Package must be granted Manifest.permission_group.PHONE permission to listen call events on Android M and above devices.
